 1. Privacy Policy                                                                                                                                       
                                                                                                                                                          
  Textcommand Privacy Policy                                                                                                                              
                                                                                                                                                          
  Last updated: February 11, 2026                                                                                                                         
                                                                                                                                                          
  Overview                                                                                                                                                
                                                                                                                                                          
  Textcommand is a text editing application designed with your privacy in mind. We do not collect, store, transmit, or share any personal information or  
  user data.                                                                                                                                              
                                                                                                                                                          
  Data Collection                                                                                                                                         
                                                                                                                                                          
  Textcommand does not collect any data. Specifically:                                                                                                    
                                                                                                                                                          
  - No Personal Information: We do not collect names, email addresses, or any identifying information.                                                    
  - No Usage Analytics: We do not track how you use the app, what features you access, or how often you use them.                                         
  - No Document Content: Your text, documents, and workbooks remain entirely on your device. We cannot access, read, or transmit your content.            
  - No Network Connections: Textcommand does not connect to the internet or any external servers.                                                         
                                                                                                                                                          
  Local Storage                                                                                                                                           
                                                                                                                                                          
  All data created within Textcommand is stored locally on your Mac:                                                                                      
                                                                                                                                                          
  - Session data is stored in your Application Support folder for session restoration                                                                     
  - Workbook files (.workbook) and text files (.txt) are saved only where you choose to save them                                                         
                                                                                                                                                          
  Third-Party Services                                                                                                                                    
                                                                                                                                                          
  Textcommand does not integrate with any third-party services, analytics platforms, or advertising networks.                                             
                                                                                                                                                          
  Children's Privacy                                                                                                                                      
                                                                                                                                                          
  Textcommand does not collect data from any users, including children under 13.                                                                          
                                                                                                                                                          
  Changes to This Policy                                                                                                                                  
                                                                                                                                                          
  If we update this privacy policy, the new policy will be posted with an updated revision date.                                                          
                                                                                                                                                          
  Contact                                                                                                                                                 
                                                                                                                                                          
  If you have questions about this privacy policy, please contact us at [nick@paytonsplace.net].                                                             
                                 
